column5: What happened, I thought we were going to get updated vids more often? I really enjoy them and hope for more.
He's busy shark fishing right now.
Ya, what Dan said. Get twitter, he still keeps contact when away!

Sorry guys I have been on the west coast and the east coast all in one week it's been crazy! A new vid will be up today. It great to hear you like them we will keep on top of them more. The best way to keep these coming is for everyone to check them out. The more views we get from here the more budget we will be allowed to put towards them so we can do more! So everyone please make sure to check them out and tell your friends to as well. Hope everyone has a great long weekend!  Dave Mercer
there's a new one up now
Sounds cool, I think the two from Gettin Hooked might of been on the same charter(most likely wrong) but if it was anything like there shar show then it's going to be a blast!
I wouldn't have known there was a new one up...the banner still says Aug. 23...thanks Rick
